@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jrmwye(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(0.34)
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.sin((tmp + 0.25 * v1 + 0.53)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.63 - v2 + 0.05)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.06 + v2 + 0.31)) + (wp.exp(v0 + 0.07) - (v2 + 0.19 - v1 + 0.02)))
    tmp = wp.cos((tmp * (v1 + 0.40 + tmp + 0.79)))
    v1 = (v2 + v1)
    data[tid] = v0
